{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, it was on average ~ 21 times faster than the physicians' group.",
    "DiscussionThree GPs and two experts independently reviewed 1,198 records and categorized them as included or excluded, which took several days.",
    "In contrast, it took ChatGPT less than one hour to do the same.",
    "ChatGPT exhibited remarkable sensitivity and NPV, both exceeding 95%.",
    "Additionally, it had the lowest false negative rates among the raters."
  ]
}